'''Emily Garfield''' (1930 - 2018) was an American wedding planner and the single mother of professional baseball player [[Perry Garfield]]. 

==Death==
Emily died while sleeping peacefully in 2018, at the age of 88. Perry cremated her and sprinkled her ashes at an Ikea. He inherited $1,670,352.
